Clanrats are the unwashed masses of the various Skaven clans. Check out how Ollie paints a Skaven Clanrat in just nine paints! Super quick-quick!

Iron Warriors

Contrast:
Black Templar
Blood Angels Red
Skeleton Horde

Stormhost Silver

Agrax Earthshade
Carroburg Crimson
Targor Rageshade
